    <p>
        Learning points
    </p>
    <p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Probability of an event is the likelihood of an event occurring.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Probability as a measure can be expressed as a fraction.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </p>
